本人造謠，只是拿出的證據反而又被日本網友嗆爆，連中國網友都看不下去。<br />\n<br />\n該名日本推主轉貼《中新網》照片，是許多中國大媽「徒手」爬上長城外牆的模樣，看起來高度不低，一失手恐怕就會喪失性命，然而冒著生命危險攀牆，卻只是為了不想付入城的票錢！超狂行徑讓該篇推文被轉推1.7萬次，還有超過2萬個喜歡，日網友也紛紛笑說「命不值錢啊」、「大媽都爬得上長城，長城到底可以防禦什麼匈奴XD」、「雖然免費但不能保證生命啊」。<br />\n<br />\n只是《觀察者網》立刻反擊，指出該照片是2011年10月的舊聞，且地點並非長城，而是南京中華門城牆，認為日本人造謠中傷中國大陸。然而該說法卻連中國網友都看不下去，紛紛回應「為逃票爬城是事實啊」、「不是長城也不能爬吧」、「一不尊重古蹟、二不尊重自己生命」、「想打臉還被自己人嗆爆」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E5%A4%AA%E7%8B%82-%E5%BE%92%E6%89%8B%E7%88%AC%E9%95%B7%E5%9F%8E%E5%9A%87%E5%A3%9E%E6%97%A5%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B-004128855.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%258B%2582-%25E5%25BE%2592%25E6%2589%258B%25E7%2588%25AC%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%259A%2587%25E5%25A3%259E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%258F%258B-004128855.html&d=Od93XWp5wLOUKSfcqLyypNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=ee5b5030\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E5%A4%AA%E7%8B%82-%E5%BE%92%E6%89%8B%E7%88%AC%E9%95%B7%E5%9F%8E%E5%9A%87%E5%A3%9E%E6%97%A5%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B-004128855.html</a>"},{"pid":"e2058bbfa2a9d9ccf9192e2b68e8f2b56d74e63d","tid":455592,"uid":70985,"like":197,"dislike":4,"score":193,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T08:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/624/d624252.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F624%2Fd624252.jpg&h=c8b2c6cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://zhongwen.astro.com.my/Portals/21/Images/BianJi_GuanLiJie_JumpBuilding/637w6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzhongwen.astro.com.my%2FPortals%2F21%2FImages%2FBianJi_GuanLiJie_JumpBuilding%2F637w6.jpg&h=69ac3060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a522ab1371f35503bdec126a1cf4a65e56c232d1","tid":455592,"uid":1